 separ file fee for each militari weapon that he ha or intend to carri the applic shall contain all of the follow inform the name age address occup and busi address of the applic if the applic is natur person or the name address and princip place of busi of the applic if the applic is corpor descript of the militari weapon for which licens is request includ the serial number and all identif mark statement of the purpos for which the militari weapon wa acquir and for which it is to be possess carri or use ani other inform that the issu author may requir in give effect to thi section the oath of the applic that the inform on the applic is true no later than the close of busi on the fourteenth day after an applic for licens to have and carri militari weapon ha been file under divis of thi section the issu author shall either approv the applic and issu licens to the applic or deni the applic and send letter of denial by ordinari mail to the applic after conduct ani necessari investig the issu author shall issu licens to an applic whom it determin satisfi the follow criteria the applic is twenti one year of age or older if the applic is natur person it appear that the applic will possess and carri the militari weapon as collector item or for legitim scientif educ industri or other proper purpos it appear that the applic ha suffici compet to have and carri the militari weapon and that proper precaut will be taken to ensur the secur of the militari weapon and the safeti of person and properti the applic otherswis is not prohibit by law from have or carri danger ordnanc licens issu pursuant to divis of thi section shall be valid for one year after the date of it issuanc the licens shall be renew pursuant to divis of thi section except as provid in divis of thi section ani person who is issu licens under divis of thi section shall renew the licens by file an applic for renew by regular mail with the sheriff of the counti or the safeti director or polic chief of the municip corpor who wa the issu author of the licens an applic for renew shall be file annual no later than one year after the date on which the licens wa issu or last renew each sheriff and each safeti director and peac offic of municip corpor shall make avail applic for the renew of licens issu under divis of thi section in the applic the applic under oath shall updat the inform submit in the previou applic for licens or the renew of licens the applic for the renew of licens shall be accompani by fee of five dollar the applic shall file seper applic for renew and pay seper renew fee for each militari weapon that he intend to continu to have and carri person who ha chang hi resid or princip place of busi to locat outsid of the jurisdict of the issu author subsequ to the issuanc or renew of licens under thi section shall renew hi licens by file an applic in the manner prescrib by divis of thi section with the sheriff of the counti or the safeti director or polic chief of the municip corpor where he then resid or ha hi princip place of busi when make an applic to renew licens after chang in resid or place of busi the applic shall give notic of the chang of address by regular mail to the origin issu author for the licens and the state fire marshal on notif form prescrib by the sheriff safeti director or polic chief from whom he seek renew licens to have and carri militari weapon shall identifi the person to whom it is issu identifi the militari weapon for which it is issu state the purpos identifi in divis of thi section for which the militari weapon will be possess and carri state it expir date and list all restrict on the have or carri of the militari weapon as prescrib by the law of thi state and applic feder law ani person who is issu licens to have and carri militari weapon under thi section and who chang hi address shall notifi the issu author of the chang of hi address no later than nineti day after the chang ha occur the issu author shall forward to the state fire marshal copi of each licens issu or renew under thi section the state fire marshal shall keep perman file of all licens issu or renew under thi section the issu author shall caus each applic fee of fifti dollar file under divis of thi section to be deposit in the gener fund of the counti or muncip corpor serv by the issu author the issu author shall caus two dollar and fifti cent of each renew fee file under divis of thi section to be deposit in the gener fund of the counti or municip corpor serv by the issu author and shall send two dollar and fifti cent of each renew fee to the treasur of state for deposit in the state treasuri to the credit of the gener revenu fund whoever violat divis of thi section is guilti of fail to appli for the licensur of militari weapon feloni of the fourth degre whoever violat divis of thi section is guilti of fail to appli for renew of licens for militari weapon misdemeanor of the first degre militari weapon that is not licens as requir by thi section is contraband as defin in section of the revis code and is subject to forfeitur under section of the revis code sec no person shall do ani of the follow import manufactur possess for sale sell or furnish to ani person ani militari weapon recklessli sell lend give furnish firearm to ani person prohibit section the revis code acquir use firearm recklessli sell lend give furnish danger ordnanc person prohibit section revis code acquir use danger ordnanc possess firearm danger ordnanc with purpos dispos violat divis thi section manufactur possess sale sell furnish to ani person law enforc agenc author use in polic work brass knuckl cestu billi blackjack sandbag switchblad knife springblad knife graviti knife or similar weapon when transfer danger ordnanc to anoth neglig fail requir transfer exhibit ani identif licens permit show be author acquir danger ordnanc pursuant section revis code neglig fail take complet record transact forthwith forward copi of the record sheriff counti safeti director po